column1: Gema: i gotta cough but I’m scared because I don’t want anyone to think I got the corona virus.

“Just placed an order” if we are always this behind in getting things done we are all doomed. If done over a month ago lives would be saved. If you let everyone get coronavirus who do you think is going to make the products we need? @realDonaldTrump is deliberately destroying us.
